text:
....?
Producer-san, what are you looking at?

Good morning, Kaho.
This is the design for the new costumes.

New costumes...!
They look like fluttering feathers...!

It's great that they're well-received.
These are meant for all of 283PRO to wear.

That's amazing!
When can we wear them!?

Well, let's see...
It might be a bit further in the future.

I see!
I hope we can wear them soon!
